|__  /  \ |__)  |\/| /__` 
|    \__/ |  \  |  | .__/ 
                          
> Forms

HTML Form --> HTTP request --> Server

"GET"       -->     retrives information from the server
"POST"      -->     sends data from a form to the server

<form action="/location" method="POST">                 <!-- specify the path the form URL information should go to -->
</form>                                                 <!--  "POST" sends data to the server -->

_________________________________________________

> Text Input box:

<form action="/location" method="POST">                 <!-- POSTing the data to the server

    <label for="username">                              <!-- adding a label on top of the text box -->
        Username:                                       <!-- label text -->
    </label> <br>                                       <!-- closing label and <br> (new line) -->
    
    <input type="text" name="username"/>                <!-- text input box -->
</form>

_________________________________________________

> Password Input box:

<form action="/location" method="POST">

    <label for="password">
        password
    </label> <br>
    
    <input type="password"/>
    <input type="submit"/>
</form>

_________________________________________________

> Checkboxes:

<form action="/location" method="POST">

    <input type="checkbox" name="Option 1" value="Option 1" />
    <label for="Option 1"> Option 1 </label> <br>
    
    <input type="checkbox" name="Option 2" value="Option 2" />
    <label for="Option 2"> Option 2 </label> <br>
</form>

_________________________________________________

> Radio Buttons:
- multiple buttons but only one can be selected 

<form action="/location" method="POST">

    <input type="radio" name="Group 1" value="Option 1" />
    <label for="Option 1"> Option 1 </label> <br>
    
    <input type="radio" name="Group 1" value="Option 2" />
    <label for="Option 2"> Option 2 </label> <br>
</form>

_________________________________________________

> TextArea:
- A text input box, but allowing mulitple lines

<form action="/location" method="POST">

    <label for="username">
        Input here:
    </label> <br>
    
    <textarea name="multiline" rows="5"> Example Text </textarea>
</form>

_________________________________________________

> Required Fields:
- Information will not submit until a required field is filled

<form action="/location" method="POST">

    <input placeholder="Name"required/> <br/>                               <!-- add "required" to the input -->
    <textarea placeholder="Password"required/> </textarea><br/>
</form>

