>> Text Methods:

p{
    color: red;
    font-family: "Courier New", monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    text-transform: uppercase;                                      /* --> uppercase,  lowercase    */
    text-decoration: underline red solid 5px;                       /* -->  underline, overline, line-through and none */
}

