>> Alignment

p {
    text-align: center;                         /* left, right, center and justify */
}                                               /* The justify alignment spreads the text out so that every line of the text has the same width */

__________________________________________________________________________________________________

/* HTML */
<div class="parent">
  <div class="child">
  </div>
</div>

/* CSS */
.parent {
  border: 4px solid red;
}

.child {
  width: 50%;
  padding: 20px;
  border: 4px solid green;
}

__________________________________________________________________________________________________

>> Target specific tags:

h2 > span {                             /* This only targets "span" tags that are inside (children) of "h2" tags
  color: #FA9F42;
  font-size: 0.75em;
}


